videos.headline: Auburn's Johnson reverses field, hurdles and dives for TD
videos.description: Auburn quarterback Sean White almost gets sacked, but completes a short pass to Kerryon Johnson, who reverses his field and runs 47 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Auburn kicker scores after fake FG
videos.description: Auburn kicker Daniel Carlson runs for a 20-yard score after the Tigers fake a field goal.
